{"tid":2461314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：集中營的歷史，我們不能遺忘。","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:18:46.000Z","uid":2054,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4e933e90a86dc8e278ae0e5c9c22f88d37c33f4b","tid":2461314,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10157379370406065/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F46251501064%2Fposts%2F10157379370406065%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=559cea1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10157379370406065/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n集中營的歷史，我們不能遺忘。<br />\n　　<br />\n每年，駐台北以色列經濟文化辦事處 Israel in Taipei 和 German Institute Taipei 德國在台協會，都會合辦「國際大屠殺紀念日」活動，一起追思當年罹難的猶太人。今年 臺灣民主基金會 Taiwan Foundation for Democracy 也首度參與合辦。<br />\n　　<br />\n大屠殺的傷痕，提醒了我們：每一個人都有責任努力，不容許這樣的悲劇再發生。<br />\n　　<br />\n經歷過威權統治的台灣，永遠不會忘記過去。我們更會積極保護人權，堅守民主不容妥協的承諾，並與國際社會齊心共築更美好、更包容、更和平的未來。<br />\n　　<br />\n👉請來Twitter看我的英文推文：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1375018833140838406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1375018833140838406&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=63550a6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiingwen%2Fstatus%2F1375018833140838406&h=c8dd7671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1375018833140838406</a>"},{"pid":"7d406324e1f29d7593873635cb3309d57132cfc0","tid":2461314,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"個timing相當有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7056950640cd5ee1738fdf27ff07560122d7f67","tid":2461314,"uid":